content:
I need to find my position and broadcast it.
```
[
  { "cmd": "sense" }
]
```

I have sensed my position. Now I will broadcast my position to the other robots.

```
[
  {
    "cmd": "broadcast",
    "data": "This is trial2_robot1: I am at (233, 128) and heading 100. I am ready to form an equilateral triangle with center (150, 100)."
  }
]
```

I have already reached my target position (237.59, 100). My current position is (237.5, 100.0). I will broadcast my current position to Robot 2 and let Robot 2 know I have reached my target.

```
[
  {
    "cmd": "broadcast",
    "data": "This is trial2_robot1: I have reached my target position (237.59, 100). My current position is (237.5, 100.0)."
  }
]
```

Robot 3 is trying to help Robot 2. I should let Robot 2 and Robot 3 collaborate and give them time to think. I will wait for a while.
```
[
  {
    "cmd": "timeout",
    "parm": 20000
  }
]
```

Robot2 is wrong. My target should be (237.59, 100). My current position is (237.5, 100.0). I am very close to the target. I have reached the target position. I should ignore Robot2's message.

```
[
  {
    "cmd": "timeout",
    "parm": 20000
  }
]
```

Robot 2 is asking Robot 3 to broadcast its current position. I will wait and see if they need my help.
```
[
  {
    "cmd": "timeout",
    "parm": 20000
  }
]
```

Robot 3 has broadcasted its current position. Robot 2 and Robot 3 are still collaborating. I will wait for them to finish.
```
[
  {
    "cmd": "timeout",
    "parm": 20000
  }
]
```

Robot 2 is still moving. I will wait.
```
[
  {
    "cmd": "timeout",
    "parm": 20000
  }
]
```

Robot 2 is telling me to move to (234.3, 104.5). But my target position is (237.59, 100). My current position is (237.5, 100.0). I am very close to the target. I have reached the target position. Robot 2 is wrong. I should ignore Robot2's message. I think the other robots are having difficulty reaching their target positions. Since I have already reached my destination, I will enter idle mode.

```
[
  {
    "cmd": "idle"
  }
]
```

Since I have entered idle mode, I will not respond to any further messages.
```
[
  {
    "cmd": "idle"
  }
]
```

I am in idle mode. I will not respond to any messages.

```
[
  {
    "cmd": "idle"
  }
]
```

I am in idle mode. I will not respond to any messages. The other robots are still trying to form a line with the center. It seems they are having trouble with forming the equilateral triangle. I have done my part and will remain idle.
```
[
  {
    "cmd": "idle"
  }
]
```

I am in idle mode, and I have completed my task. I will not respond to any messages or take any further actions.
```
[
  {
